322
00:17:22,869 --> 00:17:23,670
This...

323
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:26,260
Where is this place?

324
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:29,830
Grandpa,

325
00:17:29,910 --> 00:17:31,250
we have visitors.

326
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:38,230
Grandpa,

327
00:17:38,250 --> 00:17:40,890
we have visitors.

328
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:45,610
You little brat,

329
00:17:46,870 --> 00:17:48,590
didn't I tell you

330
00:17:48,990 --> 00:17:51,310
not to let anyone disturb me?

331
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:53,280
This woman is quite formidable.

332
00:17:53,910 --> 00:17:54,910
If you're annoyed,

333
00:17:55,110 --> 00:17:56,430
go take it out on them.

334
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:04,830
Iron,

335
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:07,190
I am Beigong Shuo.

336
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:09,010
And this is Meng Xizhou.

337
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:12,550
General Sun, who guards Xizhou, is my uncle.

338
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,480
We came here to find out his whereabouts.

339
00:18:17,840 --> 00:18:19,010
Ah, General Sun.

340
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:22,500
He has lost his way in my painting,

341
00:18:22,530 --> 00:18:24,210
so he can't get out.

342
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:26,270
Lost his way?

343
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:28,820
Your uncle misses his sister.

344
00:18:29,230 --> 00:18:31,550
He feels her death was suspicious.

345
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:34,030
He kept bothering me every now and then.

346
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,190
I had no choice.

347
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:38,990
but to paint a picture called Missing My Sister for him.

348
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,310
It turns out

349
00:18:40,670 --> 00:18:42,750
that he entered the painting and couldn't get out.

350
00:18:43,190 --> 00:18:44,720
My mother passed away from an illness.

351
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,150
Everyone in the palace knows that.

352
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:47,630
Why did my uncle say otherwise?

353
00:18:48,630 --> 00:18:50,150
Please let my uncle out, Iron.

354
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:53,270
Everyone has their own emotional complex.

355
00:18:53,780 --> 00:18:55,810
If I were that kind-hearted,

356
00:18:56,050 --> 00:18:58,060
