374
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,590
Fool!

375
00:19:35,190 --> 00:19:36,670
You're completely wrong.

376
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,990
I've seen the Demon Queen before.

377
00:19:40,010 --> 00:19:42,000
