of many lovelorn men and women.

397
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:18,470
They've struggled their whole lives,

398
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,950
just wanting an answer.

399
00:20:20,190 --> 00:20:21,750
So they asked me to paint for them

400
00:20:21,870 --> 00:20:23,550
and recreate the scenes from earlier,

401
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:24,830
so they could find answers.

402
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:25,790
However,

403
00:20:26,510 --> 00:20:28,910
only the closest family members
 of those in the paintings

404
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:30,830
can uncover the truth.

405
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:33,360
You are Li Shiyi's daughter,

406
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:36,390
naturally connected by blood 
to the Li Shiyi in the painting.

407
00:20:36,670 --> 00:20:38,440
You can restart the story from that year,

408
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:42,260
and help me find the truth 
about Li Shiyi's battle with the Demon Queen.

409
00:20:43,470 --> 00:20:44,110
So,

410
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:45,710
are you saying

411
00:20:46,170 --> 00:20:47,390
I can go into the painting

412
00:20:47,790 --> 00:20:48,820
and witness the grand spectacle

413
00:20:48,950 --> 00:20:50,830
of my father battling the Demon Queen?

414
00:20:51,330 --> 00:20:52,240
Yes, of course.

415
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:53,670
However,

416
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:55,070
he won't recognize you.

417
00:20:55,870 --> 00:20:57,000
because you'll be possessing

418
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:58,590
the body of a stranger.

419
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:01,350
Let me make it clear.

420
00:21:01,870 --> 00:21:02,990
People who enter the painting

421
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,870
but can't solve the riddle

422
00:21:05,020 --> 00:21:06,550
will end up like his uncle.

423
00:21:06,850 --> 00:21:08,410
They will be trapped inside, unable to escape,

424
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:12,070
and eventually turn into these scattered bones.

425
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:14,030
I'll go.

426
00:21:14,340 --> 00:21:14,870
I'll go.

427
00:21:14,890 --> 00:21:15,400
No, no.

428
00:21:15,430 --> 00:21:15,870
Goddess,

429
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,790
