473
00:23:07,390 --> 00:23:08,670
Twenty years ago,

474
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:10,990
the Demon Queen was killed by Li Shiyi.

475
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:13,840
The Scroll of Mountains and Seas captured thousands of demons.

476
00:23:14,190 --> 00:23:16,150
