508
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,790
My wife is heavily pregnant and about to give birth.

509
00:24:38,250 --> 00:24:38,660
Now,

510
00:24:39,020 --> 00:24:40,470
let's split up and search for her right now.

511
00:24:40,830 --> 00:24:41,670
Madam is about to give birth

512
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:42,590
