545
00:25:37,310 --> 00:25:38,640
She's happy, even with morning sickness every day.

546
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:40,430
She's truly a good mother.

547
00:25:40,750 --> 00:25:41,310
Look,

548
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,770
